        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 1285,
      "char_end": 1362
    },
    {
      "text": "thirty (30) days from the date of BacklotCars' receipt of the invoice.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 3.3,
        "width": 5.6,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 1363,
      "char_end": 1433
    },
    {
      "text": "Express payment option: invoice amount reduced by three percent (3%) of total",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 3.7,
        "width": 6.2,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 1434,
      "char_end": 1511
    },
    {
      "text": "for payment within one (1) business day of invoice receipt.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 4.1,
        "width": 4.7,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 1512,
      "char_end": 1571
    },
    {
      "text": "Storage and storage fees accrued as a result of Carrier delay are the sole",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 4.5,
        "width": 5.9,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 1572,
      "char_end": 1646
    },
    {
      "text": "responsibility of Carrier. Storage fees not to exceed $100 per day.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 4.9,
        "width": 5.4,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 1647,
      "char_end": 1714
    },
    {
      "text": "BacklotCars may withhold payment to protect itself from services not performed",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 5.3,
        "width": 6.2,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 1715,
      "char_end": 1793
    },
    {
      "text": "in accordance with this Agreement or from claims arising out of Carrier performance.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 5.7,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 1794,
      "char_end": 1878
    },
    {
      "text": "Failure to submit invoice may result in delay in payment and/or non-payment.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 6.1,
        "width": 6.1,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 1879,
      "char_end": 1955
    },
    {
      "text": "Carrier must report any delay in pickup or delivery to BacklotCars immediately.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 6.5,
        "width": 6.3,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 1956,
      "char_end": 2035
    },
    {
      "text": "Carrier shall not pick up a vehicle and hold prior to delivery to BacklotCars.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 6.9,
        "width": 6.2,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2036,
      "char_end": 2114
    },
    {
